Intro:
-------

If you are someone who doesn't make $$$ throwing around kgs in the weightroom or the platform, lifting should really be a means to an end and not the end itself. 

What you're going to say
-------------------------

When you treat training as a way to improve your movement patterns and posture *outside* of the gym, things fall into perspective and everything else looks and feels simpler. 

